OL,3,CMan who 'inspired millions' with
OL,4,Ccandid cancer reflections dies
OL,6,FTheir Chief Executive Jonathan Carter
OL,7,Fexplains: "Simon's ability to from
OL,8,Fpartnerships and build a rapport with
OL,9,Falmost everybody was absolutely
OL,10,Famazing. He allowed people to feel
OL,11,Fclose to him and that was part of his
OL,12,Fgenerosity and kindness."
OL,14,FHis selfless nature was exemplified
OL,15,Fthrough a series of candid articles
OL,16,Fthat he wrote for a local newspaper
OL,17,Ffollowing his terminal diagnosis,
OL,18,Fdetailing his treatment and
OL,19,Freflections.
