OL,6,FIn his final weeks, Simon continued to
OL,7,Fattend charity board meetings and
OL,8,Fserve in the Honorary Police.
OL,10,FHe also wrote a book, 'A Beginners
OL,11,FGuide to Dying' which will be
OL,12,Fpublished later this year, with
OL,13,Fproceeds donated to palliative care
OL,14,Fcharities.
